# Drizzle and DB Safety Rules

- Update schema source under `src/_db/drizzle/schema/**` for data model changes.
- Keep enums centralized and reused from drizzle enum files.
- Do not hand-edit generated migration snapshots/journal.
- Use transactions for coupled multi-step writes.
- For state-dependent mutations, lock/read current row state before updating.
- Keep history/audit persistence for lifecycle transitions.
